data.title: AsiaSweep 2013 - The Arun Veembur Memorial Quiz
data.meta_description: AsiaSweep 2013 - The Arun Veembur Memorial Quiz - Download as a PDF or view online for free
data.text: The document provides the rules and questions for the Arun Veembur Memorial Quiz held as part of ASIASWEEP 2013. It contains 5 rounds with a total of 141 possible points. Round 1 has 25 one-point questions. Round 2 is called "Bangalored" and is worth 15 points. Round 3 has 30 two-point questions for a total of 60 points. Round 4 is called "Stage II" and is worth 10 points. Round 5 has 31 one-point questions for a total of 31 points. Sample questions from Round 1 are provided covering topics about lakes, poets, extinct animals, horse breeds, architecture, instruments, currencies, shells, traditions, novels, and more.
